import pandas as pd

data = pd.read_csv('Ml-FZA.csv')

observed_y1 = data['true_value_y1'].values
predicted_y1 = data['predicted_value_y1'].values

observed_y2 = data['true_value_y2'].values
predicted_y2 = data['predicted_value_y2'].values

metrics_y1 = compute_advanced_metrics(observed_y1, predicted_y1)
metrics_y2 = compute_advanced_metrics(observed_y2, predicted_y2)

metrics_df = pd.DataFrame([metrics_y1, metrics_y2], index=["α-ratio", "Yield"])
print(metrics_df)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import scipy.stats as stats

fig, axes = plt.subplots(3, 2, figsize=(10, 10), dpi= 800)
plt.subplots_adjust(hspace=0.5)
save_path= 'Residual plot.png'

residuals_y1 = predicted_y1 - observed_y1
sns.residplot(x=observed_y1, y=residuals_y1, lowess=True, ax=axes[0, 0], color='darkslateblue')
axes[0, 0].set_title("Residual Plot (α-ratio)")
axes[0, 0].set_xlabel("Observed α-ratio")
axes[0, 0].set_ylabel("Residuals")

residuals_y2 = predicted_y2 - observed_y2
sns.residplot(x=observed_y2, y=residuals_y2, lowess=True, ax=axes[0, 1], color='teal')
axes[0, 1].set_title("Residual Plot (Yield)")
axes[0, 1].set_xlabel("Observed Yield")
axes[0, 1].set_ylabel("Residuals")

stats.probplot(residuals_y1, dist="norm", plot=axes[1, 0])
axes[1, 0].set_title("Q–Q Plot (α-ratio)")

stats.probplot(residuals_y2, dist="norm", plot=axes[1, 1])
axes[1, 1].set_title("Q–Q Plot (Yield)")

axes[2, 0].hist(residuals_y1, bins=20, color='darkslateblue', alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black')
axes[2, 0].set_title("Residual Histogram (α-ratio)")
axes[2, 0].set_xlabel("Residual")
axes[2, 0].set_ylabel("Frequency")

axes[2, 1].hist(residuals_y2, bins=20, color='teal', alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black')
axes[2, 1].set_title("Residual Histogram (Yield)")
axes[2, 1].set_xlabel("Residual")
axes[2, 1].set_ylabel("Frequency")


plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig('/user/fza/path/to/residual_diagnostics.png',
            dpi=800, bbox_inches='tight', transparent=False)

plt.show()
